Title: New Michael Kors Women's Parker Two Tone Bracelet Watch MK 6055
Description: Brand new Box not included Stainless steel case with a two-tone (silver and gold-tone) stainless steel bracelet. Fixed gold-tone bezel set with crystals. White dial with gold-tone hands and crystal index hour markers. Arabic numeral marks the 12 o'clock position. Minute markers around the inner ring and outer rim. Dial Type: Analog. Luminescent hands. Day of the week and date. Three multi-function sub-dials displaying: day of the week, date and 24 hours. Quartz movement. Scratch resistant mineral crystal. Pull / push crown. Solid case back. Case diameter: 33 mm. Round case shape. Band width: 16 mm. Deployment clasp. Water resistant at 50 meters / 165 feet. Functions: date, day, hour, minute, second. Casual watch style.
